{"id":599685,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【异闻观止】新华网｜-包/","date":"2018-11-16T18:08:39Z","modified":"2018-11-17T00:29:14Z","title":"【异闻观止】新华网｜ 包","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599686\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-27.jpg 664w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-27-300x196.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/1-27-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“包”</strong></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">每当我们看到这个字时</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">或许脑海中就能立刻浮现</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">恢宏宽广的场景</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">它是《水经注·河水》里</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“河水分流，包山而过”的壮美景色</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">在贾谊名篇</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">《过秦论》中，它又是</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“席卷天下，包举宇内”的过人气势</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">它还是施耐庵眼里</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“义胆包天，忠肝盖地”的雄伟气魄</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599687\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-5.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-5-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-5-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/2-5-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“包”</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">气势宏伟</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">吞吐宇宙</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599688 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"467\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>“包”</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">含义丰富</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">引人遐想</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599689 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"420\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-1.png 420w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture1-1-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">春秋战国时期群雄纷争</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">战乱和分裂</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">带来了许多痛苦与灾难</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">但在文化上却灿烂辉煌、群星闪烁</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">形成了“百家争鸣”的局面</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599691 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/5.png 663w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/5-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/5-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">先秦诸子的思想各有特色</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">儒家仁义醇厚</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">道家清静超逸</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">墨家谨严兼爱</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">法家因势严峻</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">百年间</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">诸子百家纵横捭阖</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">在高谈阔论中</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">在超然气势下</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">显示出无尽的思想魅力</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599692\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/6-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/6-10.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/6-10-300x180.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/6-10-768x462.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/6-10-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">随着时光的流逝</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">我们离这段精彩纷呈的历史</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">早已渐行渐远</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">但那些熠熠生辉的思想</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">印象深刻的场景</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">脍炙人口的故事</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">却没有随之远去</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">直至今日</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">依旧让人津津乐道</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">引人细细品味</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599693 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/7-10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/7-10.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/7-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/7-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/7-10-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-599694 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"494\" height=\"189\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2.png 494w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture2-300x115.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 494px) 100vw, 494px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">沙漠丝绸路</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">驼铃响千载</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">翻开历史的长卷</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">无数诗人惊异于</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">丝绸之路上的壮丽风景</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">它是李白笔下</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“长风几万里，吹度玉门关”的雄浑</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">是岑参眼中</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“忽如一夜春风来，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">千树万树梨花开”的旖旎</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">也是元稹心中“胡音胡骑与胡妆”的风情</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">丝绸之路的雄奇壮阔之美</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">尽显笔端</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599695 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/8.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/8-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/8-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/8-360x240.png 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">丝绸之路不仅是文人墨客</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">眼中的绝美景色</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">也是一座沟通东西方文化的桥梁</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">汉朝张骞出使西域</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">打开了中西之间的交通</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">唐宋时中西文化交流频繁</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">明代郑和七次下西洋</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">更是促进了中外文化交流</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">如今，“一带一路”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">不仅延续了中华文明开放包容的精髓</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">还赋予了古丝绸之路更多的时代内涵</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599696\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/9-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/9-4.jpg 677w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/9-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/9-4-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-599697\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture3.png 372w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Capture3-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“包容”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">是一种“大肚能容，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">容天下难容之事”的涵养</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“世事沧桑心事定，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">胸中海岳梦中飞”的度量</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">和“海纳百川，有容乃大”的胸怀</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599698 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/10-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/10-3.jpg 717w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/10-3-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/10-3-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“包容”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">是一种美德</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">也是处世的经验和待人的艺术</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">蔺相如对廉颇的包容</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">造就了一段“将相和”的佳话</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">张英谦恭礼让</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“一纸书来只为墙，</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">让他三尺又何妨”的诗句</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">成就了“六尺巷”的百年美名</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599699 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/11-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/11-3.jpg 718w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/11-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">包商银行以</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">“包容乃大，商赢天下”</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">作为其核心理念</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">用具有包商特色的</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">普惠（包容性）金融服务</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">帮助农户和小微企业茁壮成长</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">助梦致远</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-599700 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/12-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/12-2.jpg 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/12-2-220x300.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599701\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/14.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/14.png 931w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/14-300x280.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/14-768x718.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<strong>中国数字空间｜<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\">颂歌新赛季</a></strong></p>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.08.08</span> <a title=\"【网路民议】包子第一股上来割韭菜\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e8%b7%af%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8a%e6%9d%a5%e5%89%b2%e9%9f%ad%e8%8f%9c/\">【网路民议】包子第一股上来割韭菜</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2015.08.02</span> <a title=\"【网络民议】一个被宠幸了的包子的故事\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/08/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e8%a2%ab%e5%ae%a0%e5%b9%b8%e4%ba%86%e7%9a%84%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e7%9a%84%e6%95%85%e4%ba%8b/\">【网络民议】一个被宠幸了的包子的故事</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2014.02.09</span> <a title=\"新京报｜“包子”效应：已经无法阻止领导“亲民”了\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/02/%e6%96%b0%e4%ba%ac%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e6%95%88%e5%ba%94%ef%bc%9a%e5%b7%b2%e7%bb%8f%e6%97%a0%e6%b3%95%e9%98%bb%e6%ad%a2%e9%a2%86%e5%af%bc%e4%ba%b2%e6%b0%91/\">新京报｜“包子”效应：已经无法阻止领导“亲民”了</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2014.02.04</span> <a title=\"【异闻观止】”庆丰包子”旅游团 北京5日行起价4000元\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/02/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e5%ba%86%e4%b8%b0%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e6%97%85%e6%b8%b8%e5%9b%a2-%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac5%e6%97%a5%e8%a1%8c%e8%b5%b7%e4%bb%b74000%e5%85%83/\">【异闻观止】”庆丰包子”旅游团 北京5日行起价4000元</a></li>\n</ul>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[27046,13222,24420,36906,24505,24465,13793]}